<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us | YourBrand</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css">

    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-accent: #0071e3;
            --text-main: #1d1d1f;
            --text-muted: #6e6e73;
            --bg-glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            color: var(--text-main);
            background-color: #ffffff;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Hero Section - Matching Figma Layout */
        .about-hero {
            position: relative;
            height: 550px;
            background: #000 url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519389950473-47ba0277781c?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop') center/cover no-repeat;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 80px;
        }

        .hero-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0.2), rgba(0,0,0,0.6));
        }

        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            max-width: 800px;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .hero-content h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* Value Grid - Based on your Figma Blue Border Box */
        .value-section {
            padding-bottom: 80px;
        }

        .value-container {
            border: 2px solid #0071e3; /* Matching Figma's Blue Border */
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 50px 30px;
            background: #fff;
        }

        .value-card {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .value-icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--text-main);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .value-card h4 {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .value-card p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Established Section - The Apple Logo Layout */
        .story-section {
            padding: 100px 0;
            background-color: #fafafa;
        }

        .story-image-box {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 30px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 60px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
            min-height: 400px;
        }

        .story-image-box i {
            font-size: 8rem;
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        .story-content h2 {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .story-content p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .btn-discover {
            padding: 12px 35px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            background: var(--text-main);
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-discover:hover {
            background: #000;
            transform: scale(1.05);
            color: white;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .about-hero { height: 400px; }
            .value-container { border: 1px solid #0071e3; margin: 0 10px; }
            .story-content { text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; }
            .story-image-box { min-height: 300px; padding: 40px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header><%- include("../partials/header.ejs") %></header>

    <section class="about-hero">
        <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
        <div class="hero-content">
            <span class="text-uppercase fw-bold small tracking-widest opacity-75 d-block mb-3">Our Journey</span>
            <h1>Designed for Excellence.<br>Built for You.</h1>
            <p class="lead opacity-90">We bring the future of technology to your doorstep with unmatched care and quality.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="value-section container">
        <div class="value-container">
            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="value-card">
                        <div class="value-icon"><i class="bi bi-truck"></i></div>
                        <h4>Free Shipping</h4>
                        <p>Enjoy complimentary doorstep delivery on every order, because great tech shouldn't cost extra to reach you.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="value-card">
                        <div class="value-icon"><i class="bi bi-headset"></i></div>
                        <h4>24/7 Support</h4>
                        <p>Our expert team is always here to help you navigate your new devices, day or night.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="value-card">
                        <div class="value-icon"><i class="bi bi-shield-check"></i></div>
                        <h4>Secure Payments</h4>
                        <p>Your transactions are protected by industry-leading encryption. Shop with absolute peace of mind.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="story-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row align-items-center g-5">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="story-image-box">
                        <i class="bi bi-apple"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 story-content">
                    <h2 class="text-dark">Established Since 2024</h2>
                    <p>What started as a vision to simplify tech access has grown into a community of innovators. Our focus remains on curating the world's most premium devices while providing a shopping experience that feels as high-end as the products themselves.</p>
                    <p>Every milestone we've reached since 2024 reflects our commitment to your satisfaction. From seamless logistics to a dedicated support ecosystem, we are here to empower your digital life.</p>
                    <a href="/shop" class="btn btn-discover">Shop Collection</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer><%- include("../partials/footer.ejs") %></footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>